dct_title_s: Bernards Township, Somerset County, New Jersey 1953
dct_description_sm: Road map of the Township of Bernards, Somerset County, New Jersey. Original printing in 1953, revised in 1967 by L. Stanley Stires, township engineer. Map drafted from Stires' data by General Drafting Company, Incorporated of Convent Station, N.J. Includes inset maps of Basking Ridge and Liberty Corner.
